<li>Thinking of you and your family during this difficult time.  May your memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and love as you grieve the loss of your beloved companion.</li>
<li>I am so sorry for your loss.  Your pet will always be remembered.</li>
<li>Your pet held a special place in your hearts, and that love will endure.</li>
<li>May the beautiful memories of your pet bring you solace.</li>
<li>Words cannot express how sorry I am for your loss.</li>
<li>Your pet was a lucky one to have such a loving family.</li>
